<SECOND>AM-Ritual Slayings,0271</SECOND>
<HEAD>Family Holds Quiet Funeral For Accused Cult Leader</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MIAMI (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 Family members and a handful of friends attended funeral services Sunday for the man authorities say was the `` godfather'' of a cult linked to at least 15 slayings on the U.S.-Mexican border, a relative said. The body of <PERSON> Adolfo </PERSON> <PERSON> de </PERSON> <PERSON> Jesus </PERSON> <PERSON> Constanzo </PERSON>, 26, arrived in <LOCATION> Miami </LOCATION> late Saturday night and was cremated for the funeral Sunday, <PERSON> Constanzo </PERSON>'s brother <PERSON> Fausto </PERSON> told <ORGANIZATION> WQBA </ORGANIZATION> radio in <LOCATION> Miami </LOCATION> `` It was always his wish to be cremated,'' said <PERSON> Fausto </PERSON> <PERSON> Constanzo </PERSON>, who said only that relatives and close friends were invited to the funeral. He revealed no other details about the services. `` It was a decision of ours to be so private,'' he said. `` We do n't want anyone there that does n't belong there to curse the funeral.'' <PERSON> Constanzo </PERSON> has been described as the leader of a sect that authorities blame for at least 15 killings outside the border city of <LOCATION> Matamoros </LOCATION>. Sect members have said some slayings were ritual killings while others were drug-related. Authorities had sought <PERSON> Constanzo </PERSON> and his female companion <PERSON> Sara </PERSON> <PERSON> Aldrete </PERSON> <PERSON> Villarreal </PERSON>, 24, since the discovery of the first of the bodies on a border ranch in April. Some bodies had been mutilated, with brains and organs removed. <PERSON> Aldrete </PERSON> and other sect members have said publicly that <PERSON> Constanzo </PERSON> ordered his own execution and the killing of his right-hand man, <PERSON> Martin </PERSON> <PERSON> Quintana </PERSON> <PERSON> Rodriguez </PERSON>, on May 6 when police moved in on their <LOCATION> Mexico </LOCATION> <LOCATION> City </LOCATION> apartment earlier this month. An autopsy showed <PERSON> Constanzo </PERSON> died from multiple gunshot wounds to the head and upper body.
